{"tid":404213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺16歲仔伙同黨搶劫　警召家長到場了解","createTime":"2017-09-18T02:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:47:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de15e9eaa455336c853eb7b7fc5427b9517da8bc","tid":404213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505698077_ff8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505698077_ff8c.jpg&h=c75fb052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170918/large/1505698079_8304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170918%2Flarge%2F1505698079_8304.jpg&h=ac775f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上7時52分，一名男子途經粉嶺名都地下停車場時，遭兩名戴口罩賊，從暗處閃出，搶去他的背囊。事主不甘損失尾隨追捕，跑到100米外港鐵站對開，得熱心途人協助，將其中一名賊人按地制服，報警拘捕，其同黨則逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場經初步調查，證實被捕疑犯年僅16歲，並在地面撿獲相信是賊人遺下的口罩。警方隨即聯絡到疑犯的母親到場了解事件，疑犯報稱不適送院治理。警員正設法追捕在逃疑犯。"},{"pid":"17fe75c5de7375940db66ab75e349c6d9d2b1ee2","tid":404213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223851&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223851%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Mcz9M%2FyZoDcXS3Cg2jQswZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fe73c07c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223851%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=95ecb2f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223851&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=